function Start(flTimeRemaining)

	if (gate_hasNotFailed) then
		local wave1 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CAMP_SnakeCultist_Gate_Wave1")
		for i, idTarget in ipairs(wave1) do	
			Hydra.ActorEnable(idTarget);
		end
		
		local wave1Petrify = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CAMP_SnakeCultist_Gate_Monsters_Petrify_Group1")
		ShuffleTable(wave1Petrify)
		for i, idPetrify in ipairs(wave1Petrify) do	
			Hydra.BuffRemove(S_POWER_FREEZE, "FREEZE", idPetrify)
			Hydra.Wait(3)
		end
	end
end
